# Default-deny: keep the backend build context small. Anything the
# Dockerfile COPYs is allow-listed below.
*

# Backend service needs these:
!backend/
!src/
!data/catalog/
!data/gold/
!data/silver/
!data/bronze/
!data/reference/

# Strip caches and local-only artifacts even inside allowed dirs
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.venv
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
backend/data
data/catalog/*.bak*

# Never ship secrets
**/.env
